To configure a 6to4 tunnel, modify the configuration file
${PKG_SYSCONFDIR}/hf6to4.conf for your system, then run

	${PREFIX}/sbin/hf6to4 -v start

You should then be able to ping6 www.kame.net.

===========================================================================
